    <a href="http://flask.pocoo.org">
     Flask
    </a>
    microframework.
   </p>
   <p>
    The goal of the tutorial series is to develop a decently featured microblogging application that demonstrating total lack of originality I have decided to call
    <code>
     microblog
    </code>
    .
   </p>
