        @sh4nks: sqlalchemy puts the fields of the auxiliary table inside a variable named "c", which is short for "columns". See the following page for the documentation: http://docs.sqlalchemy.org/en/rel_0_8/core/schema.html#accessing-tables-and-columns
       </p>
